  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate :

        -  acute effects of a single dose of 8 mg rosiglitazone (therapeutic dose)

        -  on insulin secretion and

        -  insulin sensitivity in 12 healthy male subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
